{
  "texts": [
    "Some people prefer to get an actionable explanation, such as 'increase your income with $X'.",
    "This actionability is not uniform over all decision subjects.",
    "Therefore, providing multiple explanations increases the chance that one explanation is useful for this specific user.",
    "Bordt et al. (2022) examine when ambiguity in explanations is problematic.",
    "They differentiate between a cooperative and adversarial context."
  ]
}